      "full_name": "JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant’s primary activity is maintenance of T-72 main battle tanks and BMP-2 amphibious infantry fighting vehicles. The plant is part of the High Precision Systems holding company of Rostec. Various models of BMP-2 infantry fighting vehicles and T-72 main battle tanks are used by the Russian army in the war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC 163 Armor Repair Plant set a record in maintenance of BMP-2 in 2023.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}